---
layout: memorial
permalink: /libations/andrew-joseph-jr/memorial-program/
title: "In Loving Memory — Andrew Joseph Jr."
description: "A Celebration of the Life of Andrew Joseph Jr. — Rapid Response Coordinator, Black Lives Matter Grassroots. Father. Educator. Advocate. Organizer."
---
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Newsreader:ital,opsz,wght@0,6..72,300;0,6..72,400;0,6..72,500;0,6..72,600;0,6..72,700;1,6..72,300;1,6..72,400;1,6..72,500&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

<style>
:root {
    /* warm near-black paper, ivory ink, burnished gold rules, restrained oxblood accent */
    --paper:       #110D0A;
    --paper-deep:  #1A1410;
    --paper-elev:  #221A14;
    --ink:         #ECE0C7;
    --ink-soft:    #A89A7E;
    --ink-faint:   #6E624B;
    --rule:        #5A4B33;
    --gold:        #B68B4E;   /* burnished, never bright */
    --gold-deep:   #8C6633;
    --oxblood:     #9B2A22;   /* his red — muted, present */
    --oxblood-deep:#5F1812;
    --hairline:    rgba(236, 224, 199, 0.14);
    --hairline-strong: rgba(236, 224, 199, 0.24);
    --page-w:      8.5in;
    --page-h:      11in;
    --margin-x:    0.85in;
    --margin-y:    0.85in;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body { background: #050402; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: "Newsreader", Georgia, serif;
    color: var(--ink);
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
    padding: 36px 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(1200px 800px at 50% -10%, #0c0a08 0%, #050402 60%, #000 100%);
  }

  .doc {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 28px;
  }

  .page {
    width: var(--page-w);
    height: var(--page-h);
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, #131009 0%, #100B07 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.7), 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.025);
    padding: var(--margin-y) var(--margin-x);
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  /* film grain — restrained, adds gravitas */
  .page::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(rgba(255, 240, 210, 0.025) 1px, transparent 1px),
      radial-gradient(rgba(255, 240, 210, 0.018) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 3px 3px, 7px 7px;
    background-position: 0 0, 1px 2px;
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
  /* deckle/vignette */
  .page::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(120% 90% at 50% 40%, transparent 55%, rgba(0,0,0,0.45) 100%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .page > * { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  /* Common type */
  .eyebrow {
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 9.5pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  .folio {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0.45in;
    left: var(--margin-x);
    right: var(--margin-x);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 8pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
  }
  .folio .ornament { color: var(--oxblood); letter-spacing: 0.4em; }

  .hairline-rule { height: 1px; background: var(--hairline); border: 0; margin: 0; }
  .gold-rule { height: 1px; background: var(--gold); border: 0; opacity: 0.85; }

  /* drop cap */
  .body-prose p { font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 1.65; margin: 0 0 0.85em; color: var(--ink-soft); text-wrap: pretty; }
  .body-prose p.lead { font-size: 13pt; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--ink); }
  .body-prose strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }
  .body-prose .dropcap::first-letter {
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: italic;
    initial-letter: 3 2;
    -webkit-initial-letter: 3 2;
    color: var(--oxblood);
    margin-right: 0.12em;
    line-height: 0.9;
  }

  /* ========== Page 1 — Cover ========== */
  .cover {
    padding: 0;
    background: #0A0705;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 1fr;
  }
  .cover .photo {
    position: relative;
    background: #0c0a07;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cover .photo img {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: 50% 22%;
    filter: contrast(1.04) saturate(0.78) brightness(0.95);
  }
  .cover .photo::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.10) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.0) 30%, rgba(0,0,0,0.55) 100%),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,0,0,0) 70%, rgba(10,7,5,0.92) 100%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(95,24,18,0.08), rgba(0,0,0,0) 40%);
  }
  .cover .photo-caption {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 24px; left: 26px; right: 26px;
    color: rgba(236, 224, 199, 0.7);
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 7.5pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .cover .text-pane {
    padding: 0.95in 0.7in 0.7in;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #120E0A 0%, #0C0805 100%);
  }
  .cover .crest {
    width: 26px; height: 26px;
    border: 1px solid var(--oxblood);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    margin-bottom: 22px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .cover .crest::after {
    content: ""; position: absolute; inset: 5px;
    background: var(--oxblood);
  }
  .cover .in-memoriam {
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 10pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.5em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.65in;
  }
  .cover h1 {
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 56pt;
    line-height: 0.95;
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .cover h1 .first { display: block; font-style: italic; font-weight: 300; font-size: 28pt; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom: 0.18em;}
  .cover h1 .last  { display: block; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink); }
  .cover h1 .suffix { display: block; font-weight: 300; font-style: italic; font-size: 26pt; color: var(--oxblood); margin-top: 0.16em; letter-spacing: 0.02em;}

  .cover .dates {
    margin-top: 0.55in;
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 13pt;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .cover .dates .em { color: var(--oxblood); margin: 0 0.45em; }

  .cover .quote {
    margin-top: auto;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline-strong);
    padding-top: 18px;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 13pt;
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .cover .quote .attrib {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-style: normal;
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 8.5pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.24em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
  }
  .cover .imprint {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0.5in; left: 0.7in; right: 0.7in;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline;
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 7.5pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
  }

  /* ========== Page 2 — Order of Service ========== */
  .page-header {
    display: flex; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    padding-bottom: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 38px;
  }
  .page-header .marque {
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 9pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.36em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
  }
  .page-title {
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 38pt;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .page-title em { color: var(--oxblood); font-weight: 400; }
  .page-title .ornament {
    color: var(--oxblood);
    font-style: normal;
    margin: 0 0.25em;
    font-size: 0.55em;
    vertical-align: 0.35em;
  }
  .subhed {
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 9pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  .service-grid {
    margin-top: 28px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 0;
  }
  .service-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2.6in 1fr auto;
    align-items: baseline;
    padding: 12px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--hairline);
  }
  .service-row .order {
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 7.5pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-feature-settings: "tnum";
  }
  .service-row .item {
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-size: 13pt;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .service-row .item .note { color: var(--ink-soft); font-style: italic; font-size: 11pt; margin-left: 8px; }
  .service-row .by {
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 11pt;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    text-align: right;
  }
  .service-row .by.placeholder { color: var(--gold); opacity: 0.55; }

  .service-foot {
    margin-top: 38px;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 36px;
  }
  .service-foot h4 {
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 8.5pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin: 0 0 8px;
  }
  .service-foot p {
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-size: 12pt;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .service-foot .placeholder { color: var(--ink-faint); font-style: italic; }

  /* ========== Page 3 — Obituary ========== */
  .obit-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2.8in 1fr;
    gap: 36px;
    margin-top: 32px;
    height: calc(100% - 1.4in);
  }
  .obit-side {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    gap: 18px;
  }
  .portrait {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    background-color: #1b150c;
    filter: contrast(1.04) saturate(0.78);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .portrait img {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .portrait::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,0,0,0) 60%, rgba(0,0,0,0.45) 100%);
  }
  .portrait.fist img { object-position: 50% 25%; }
  .portrait.banner img { object-position: 50% 28%; }
  .portrait.paver img { object-position: 50% 20%; }
  .portrait.rally img { object-position: 50% 30%; }
  .portrait.family { aspect-ratio: 4/3; }
  .portrait.family img { object-position: 50% 30%; }
  .caption {
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 8pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .caption .num {
    color: var(--oxblood);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-right: 0.6em;
  }

  .obit-main { padding-top: 4px; }
  .obit-main h2 {
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 21pt;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .obit-main h2 em { color: var(--oxblood); font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; }

  /* Pullquote */
  .pull {
    margin: 20px 0;
    padding: 18px 22px;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--oxblood);
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(155,42,34,0.06) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0) 100%),
      var(--paper-deep);
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 14pt;
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .pull cite {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-style: normal;
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 8.5pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  /* ========== Tribute spreads ========== */
  .tribute-hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
    gap: 36px;
    align-items: start;
    margin-top: 28px;
  }
  .tribute-hero .big-quote {
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 26pt;
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .tribute-hero .big-quote .accent { color: var(--oxblood); }

  .columns-2 {
    column-count: 2;
    column-gap: 0.5in;
    column-rule: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    margin-top: 30px;
  }
  .columns-2 p { font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--ink-soft); margin: 0 0 0.8em; text-wrap: pretty; }
  .columns-2 p.lead { font-size: 12.5pt; color: var(--ink); }
  .columns-2 .section {
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 8.5pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin: 1em 0 0.4em;
    break-after: avoid;
  }
  .columns-2 .dropcap::first-letter {
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--oxblood);
    initial-letter: 3;
    -webkit-initial-letter: 3;
    margin-right: 0.12em;
    line-height: 0.9;
  }

  /* ========== Timeline page ========== */
  .timeline {
    margin-top: 30px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.4in 1fr;
    gap: 0 24px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .timeline::before {
    content: ""; position: absolute;
    top: 8px; bottom: 8px;
    left: 1.4in; width: 1px;
    background: var(--hairline);
  }
  .tl-year {
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 9pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    padding-top: 14px;
    padding-bottom: 14px;
    text-align: right;
    padding-right: 24px;
    position: relative;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline);
  }
  .tl-year:first-child, .tl-year + .tl-year { border-top-color: transparent; }
  .tl-event {
    padding-top: 14px;
    padding-bottom: 14px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    position: relative;
  }
  .tl-event::before {
    content: ""; position: absolute;
    left: -28px; top: 22px;
    width: 9px; height: 9px;
    background: var(--oxblood);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px #0e0a07;
  }
  .tl-event h3 {
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 13pt;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 4px;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .tl-event p {
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-size: 10.5pt;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ========== Scripture page ========== */
  .scripture {
    padding: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(80% 60% at 50% 40%, #1A130C 0%, #0A0705 100%);
    position: relative;
  }
  .scripture .center {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    padding: 1.2in 1.4in;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; text-align: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .scripture .ornament-top {
    color: var(--oxblood);
    letter-spacing: 1em;
    font-size: 11pt;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }
  .scripture .label {
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 9pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .scripture h2 {
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 36pt;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 6px;
  }
  .scripture .citation {
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 11pt;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  .scripture .verse {
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-size: 14pt;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--ink);
    max-width: 4.6in;
  }
  .scripture .verse .stanza { margin-bottom: 1em; }
  .scripture .colophon {
    margin-top: 38px;
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 8pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  /* ========== Reflections page ========== */
  .reflections-stack {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    gap: 36px;
    margin-top: 38px;
  }
  .reflect {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.55in 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .reflect .num {
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 36pt;
    color: var(--oxblood);
    line-height: 0.9;
    text-align: right;
    padding-top: 4px;
  }
  .reflect .body blockquote {
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 19pt;
    line-height: 1.35;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
  .reflect .body .attrib {
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 8.5pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.24em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
  }
  .reflect .body .attrib .when { color: var(--gold); }

  /* ========== Acknowledgements / Closing ========== */
  .ack-grid {
    margin-top: 28px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 36px;
  }
  .ack-block h3 {
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 9pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline);
  }
  .ack-block p { font-family: "Newsreader", serif; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--ink-soft); margin: 0 0 8px; text-wrap: pretty; }
  .pallbearers { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 8px 22px; }
  .pallbearers li {
    list-style: none;
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-size: 12pt;
    color: var(--ink);
    padding: 6px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--hairline);
  }
  .pallbearers { padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .placeholder-name { color: var(--ink-faint); font-style: italic; }
  .honorary {
    margin: 0; padding: 0; list-style: none;
  }
  .honorary li {
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-size: 11.5pt;
    color: var(--ink);
    padding: 6px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--hairline);
  }

  .closing {
    margin-top: 36px;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 30px 0 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--oxblood);
  }
  .closing .crest {
    width: 24px; height: 24px;
    border: 1px solid var(--oxblood);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    margin: 0 auto 18px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .closing .crest::after {
    content: ""; position: absolute; inset: 4px;
    background: var(--oxblood);
  }
  .closing p.benediction {
    font-family: "Newsreader", serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 17pt;
    line-height: 1.35;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
  .closing p.signoff {
    margin-top: 18px;
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 9pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  /* ========== Tribute page 2 — quotebox + image ========== */
  .tribute-final {
    margin-top: 28px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 36px;
  }
  .tribute-final .col-img {
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    filter: contrast(1.04) saturate(0.78);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .tribute-final .col-img img {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
